overview: Foot Centers of North Carolina is a state of the art podiatry practice serving the Piedmont Triad area. With four doctors on staff and a wide variety of on-site services offered, you won’t need to worry about traveling from place to place to have tests done. The Foot Centers of NC has on-site x-ray and ultrasound for testing and offers services for both adults and children. If you have foot problems, we can help. Make an appointment today with one of our trained and friendly staff.
